Name: Womb Room
About the game: Welcome to the Womb Room , the beginning of the end. Key Features: How will you live your life? Is it even up to you? Will you make it out of the womb? Is it a good idea to play with Dad's gun? How long will you last? Was life worth living? Why does that blood stained Pomeranian want you dead? Who controls your destiny? I bet that blue stuff under the sink tastes great! Is there a God? Contract a life threatening illness! Puppets! WORKSHOP 47 Achievements! Steam Trading Cards! Would you do it all over again? Womb Room might answer all these questions and more! It's time to live the life you never asked for. 'It's time to die!'
